sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Git as GitHub / GitLab
    participant CI as CI Runner
    participant VG as Valk Guard
    participant PR as Pull Request

    Dev->>Git: Push Code
    Git->>CI: Trigger Pipeline
    CI->>VG: valk-guard scan . --format sarif
    
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        note right of VG: Scanning
        VG->>VG: Parse Source Files
        VG->>VG: Extract/Synthesize SQL
        VG->>VG: Check Rules
    end
    
    alt Issues Found
        VG-->>CI: Exit Code 1 (Findings)
        CI->>Git: Upload SARIF Report
        Git->>PR: Annotate Code with Errors
        CI-->>Dev: Build Failed (Block Merge)
    else Clean
        VG-->>CI: Exit Code 0
        CI-->>Dev: Build Passed
    end
